 8пёҸвғЈ IAM Policy Evaluation Logic (VERY IMPORTANT рҹ”Ҙ)

 вқ— Golden Rule:

For every API call, decision STARTS WITH DENY

 Step-by-Step Evaluation

 Step 1пёҸвғЈ

вҶ’ AWS saari applicable policies ko combine karta hai
(IAM policy + resource policy + SCP, etc.)

 Step 2пёҸвғЈ

вҶ’ Agar ANY explicit DENY mil gaya
рҹ‘ү Final decision = DENY вқҢ

 Step 3пёҸвғЈ

вҶ’ Agar DENY nahi hai aur ALLOW match karta hai
рҹ‘ү Final decision = ALLOW вң…

 Step 4пёҸвғЈ

вҶ’ Agar kuch bhi match nahi karta
рҹ‘ү Default = DENY вқҢ

рҹ“Ң Explicit DENY always wins

---

 9пёҸвғЈ Evolution of Policy (Real-World Logic)

Airplane example вңҲпёҸ:

1пёҸвғЈ Passenger boarding
2пёҸвғЈ Check вҶ’ Is person on NO-FLY list?
вҶ’ Yes вқҢ вҶ’ DENY
3пёҸвғЈ No вҶ’ Valid documents?
вҶ’ Yes вң… вҶ’ ALLOW
4пёҸвғЈ No вҶ’ DENY

рҹ‘ү Same logic AWS IAM follow karta hai

---

 рҹ”ҹ Key Interview Points (Must Remember)

вҶ’ IAM policy is JSON based
вҶ’ Default action is always DENY
вҶ’ Explicit DENY > Allow
вҶ’ Managed policy > Inline policy (best practice)
вҶ’ Resource policy used for cross-account access
вҶ’ Policies control authorization, not authentication

